</h3>
<p>
 Our
 <a href="http://salrc.uchicago.edu/grants/awards/index.shtml">
  Awards
 </a>
 page containing information on grants for materials development given out by SALRC in the last four years is now a database searchable by language.
</p>
<h3>
 SALRC Recommended Fonts
</h3>
<p>
 As a resource for language teaching faculty, students, and SALRC-affiliated software developers, the SALRC is 
                assembling a collection of fonts that we believe are best suited for displaying South Asian 
                languages on the computer screen. This site provides practical information about these fonts, 
                including text samples, how and where to get them, and how to install and use them on your computer.
</p>
<p>
 <a href="/resources/fonts/">
  Read More &gt;&gt;
 </a>
</p>
